00:15:41.967 --> 00:15:47.397
For me it was the beautiful stained glass that took my breath away and left me wanting more.

00:15:48.047 --> 00:15:51.717
We will be returning as will our children and their children's children.”

00:15:53.167 --> 00:15:58.067
